{"id":343176,"date":[{"year":1957,"month":3,"day":1}],"page":"3","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"","column":"思想漫步","genre":"","count":"61","ytitle":"","mtitle":"金子","ftitle":"","authors":[],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"发光的东西不都是金子。同样的，漂亮的、动听的、矫饰的言词不都是良言。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有一句话说得好:一切真理都是简朴的。　(宁)"}]}